<subSubSection pageId="59" pageNumber="60" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="59.[151,1437,1029,1308]" pageId="59" pageNumber="60">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,353,1101,1127]" pageId="59" pageNumber="60">Distribution.</emphasis>
Siberian-Far Eastern, subboreal. From 
<collectingRegion box="[797,853,1101,1127]" country="Russia" name="Altay" pageId="59" pageNumber="60">Altai</collectingRegion>
to Primorye and 
<collectingRegion box="[1051,1149,1101,1127]" country="Russia" name="Sakhalin" pageId="59" pageNumber="60">Sakhalin</collectingRegion>
Isl.. Outside of 
<collectingCountry box="[1332,1407,1101,1127]" name="Russia" pageId="59" pageNumber="60">Russia</collectingCountry>
in NE and N 
<collectingCountry box="[270,340,1137,1163]" name="China" pageId="59" pageNumber="60">China</collectingCountry>
, N 
<collectingCountry box="[378,450,1138,1164]" name="South Korea" pageId="59" pageNumber="60">Korea</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="59.[151,1437,1029,1308]" box="[199,695,1173,1200]" pageId="59" pageNumber="60">
