<taxonomicName authority="(Beljaev 2016)" baseAuthorityName="Beljaev" baseAuthorityYear="2016" box="[345,691,1173,1200]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Grossulariaceae" genus="Ribes" kingdom="Plantae" order="Saxifragales" pageId="59" pageNumber="60" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="dikuscha">
<emphasis box="[345,514,1173,1199]" italics="true" pageId="59" pageNumber="60">Ribes dikuscha</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Beljaev, E. A." box="[528,683,1173,1200]" pageId="59" pageNumber="60" refId="ref91599" refString="Beljaev, E. A. (2016) Fam. Geometridae - Pyadenitzi. In: Lelei, A. S. (Ed.), Annotated catalogue of the insects of Russian Far East. Vol. 2. Lepidoptera. Dal'nauka, Vladivostok, pp. 518 - 666. [in Russian]" type="book" year="2016">Beljaev 2016</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="59.[151,1437,1029,1308]" pageId="59" pageNumber="60">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,262,1209,1235]" pageId="59" pageNumber="60">Note.</emphasis>
Recently, 
<taxonomicName authorityName=": Makhov &amp; Beljaev" authorityYear="2019" box="[379,538,1209,1236]" class="Insecta" family="Geometridae" genus="Abraxas" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="59" pageNumber="60" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="karafutonis">
<emphasis box="[379,538,1209,1236]" italics="true" pageId="59" pageNumber="60">A. karafutonis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was found in the nature reserve “Tigireksky’’, 
<collectingRegion box="[1058,1114,1209,1235]" country="Russia" name="Altay" pageId="59" pageNumber="60">Altai</collectingRegion>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Naydenov, A. E. &amp; Yakovlev, R. V." pageId="59" pageNumber="60" pagination="255 - 261" refId="ref95667" refString="Naydenov, A. E. &amp; Yakovlev, R. V. (2018) New discoveries of Geometridae on the territory of the State Nature Reserve &quot; Tigireksky &quot;, West Altai, Russia (Lepidoptera: Geometridae). SHILAP Revista de Lepidopterologia, 46 (182), 255 - 261." type="journal article" year="2018">Naydenov, Yakovlev, 2018: 256</bibRefCitation>
, 260: incorrect identification as “ 
<taxonomicName authorityName=": Staudinger &amp; Rebel" authorityYear="1901" box="[567,816,1245,1271]" class="Insecta" family="Geometridae" genus="Abraxas" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="59" pageNumber="60" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="grossulariata">
<emphasis box="[567,816,1245,1271]" italics="true" pageId="59" pageNumber="60">Abraxas grossulariata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
L.”). This locality should be treated as the westernmost border of the range of 
<taxonomicName authorityName=": Makhov &amp; Beljaev" authorityYear="2019" box="[402,561,1281,1308]" class="Insecta" family="Geometridae" genus="Abraxas" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="59" pageNumber="60" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="karafutonis">
<emphasis box="[402,561,1281,1308]" italics="true" pageId="59" pageNumber="60">A. karafutonis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
